⦿ .spun — the five-fold spin of Setzer Gabbiani
node FF6 · FF6 · ⟦Setzer Gabbiani:FF6:f4fc4e⟧

WHO   — Setzer Gabbiani — the gambler
WHAT  — The airship captain of Final Fantasy VI — a man of dice, slots, and luck who joins the Returners when Celes wagers his own heart against him, and lends his ship and his nerve to a world worth gambling on.
WHERE — FF6 · Final Fantasy VI  Framework inputs: Final Fantasy VI (America's Final Fantasy III, 1994)  Conductor / external anchor: ROOT0 (catalogued into UD0)
WHY   — Because a man who has lost everything that mattered can still choose what he risks next; because freedom is the only stake worth the open sky; because love, like a coin, falls how it falls — and you play the hand you are dealt.
HOW   — By the Blackjack and later the Falcon, by loaded and honest dice alike, by slots and sleight and the cold steel of his cards — and by the gambler's nerve that does not flinch when the odds turn against the whole world.

awareness — what the node knows of itself:
  Life's a game of chance — and I'd rather lose it flying free than win it on the ground.

